high_descs: Turn to the left, walk forward, then turn left again and go to the stove.
Pick up the potato from the counter next to the stove.
Turn around and walk across the kitchen, then turn left and face the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the potato in, then take the potato back out.
Turn left, walk forward, turn right towards the coffee maker.
Set the potato on the counter in front of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Take the potato, put it in the fridge and set it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the potato off of the counter.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then hang a left and walk up to the fridge.
Put the potato in the fridge for a couple seconds to let it get cold then take it out and close the fridge.
Turn left and walk towards the microwave, then turn right to face the counter with the coffee machine on it.
Put the chilled potato on the counter in front of the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled potato on the counter.
